Yum! I used Tabasco's Sweet and Spicy in place of the Thai sauce. My friends and I like it so much that I don't cut back the recipe for the cornstarch and veggie broth... that way I can have it again and again (and when I get sick of the spicy flavor I play around with other spices with the same broth base or other veggies like zucchini and carrots).

